texts.main: Hi 👋🏽, my name is Thea Jenny E. Kolnes ✨
texts.about: I'm currently studying Computer Technology 💻 at University in Bergen and Western Norway University of Applied Sciences.

projects.title: Programming Language
projects.description: Me and Vetle Knutsen created our own programing language CA$H with ANTLR. Created an interpreter and compiler in the special course DAT259 at HVL.

projects.title: Melbourne Dagbok🇦🇺
projects.description: My travel blog from my exchange semester in Australia, Melbourne. During my travels I uploaded posts and pictures of my life down under. This website uses sanity and tailwindCSS in React.

projects.title: Memories🎞️
projects.description: Website for uploading my pictures that I am proud of via sanity. This website is built in React and tailwindCSS.

projects.title: echo Webkom👩🏽‍💻
projects.description: Webkom is a sub-group of our student association under the Department of Informatics at University in Bergen. Webkom runs the student association's websites.
